script = ExtResource("1_4q7uc")
ref_name = "Space Telescope Imaging Spectrograph"
ref_desc = "[b][color=light_blue]Section:[/color] 3.4[/b]
The STIS is multifunctional spectrograph that uses a combination of sensors (one CCD and two MAMA) and is the complement to COS.
Where the COS deals with UV the STIS deals with everything else."
wavelength_low = 115.0
wavelength_high = 1030.0
